OL,3,CTFL fares to rise by 5.8 % - that's
OL,4,Cmore than the rate of inflation
OL,6,FUnderground and Overground fares will
OL,7,Frise by more than the rate of
OL,8,Finflation despite a fares freeze on
OL,9,Fthe rest of the rail network.
OL,11,FSir Sadiq Khan confirmed the 5.8 per
OL,12,Fcent increase from March 2026.
OL,14,FBus and tram fares will be frozen
OL,15,Fagain, for the seventh time and be
OL,16,Fsubsidised by the City Hall budget.
OL,18,FThe hike means prices will go up by
OL,19,Ffive to 20 pence or more, depending on
OL,20,Fwhen and where you are travelling.
