OL,3,CTFL fares to rise by 5.8 % - that's
OL,4,Cmore than the rate of inflation
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London, Sir Sadiq Khan,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I remain committed to doing
OL,8,Feverything in my power to keep TfL
OL,9,Ffares as affordable as possible
OL,10,Fbecause I know how the cost-of-living
OL,11,Fcrisis is still hitting many Londoners
OL,12,Fhard.
OL,14,F"That's why I'm announcing plans for
OL,15,Fan emergency cost-of-living measure,
OL,16,Ffunded by City Hall, to continue
OL,17,Ffreezing bus and tram fares until July
OL,18,F2026.
